Pokemon App

(Condition) The user can login

As a user, I can login with username and password.
As a user, I can be prevented from moving forward if the EditText fields are blank.
As a logged in user, I can have symbols and other data types inside my username and password.
As a logged in user, I am kept logged in on the device.
As a logged in user, I will be taken to the loading screen followed by the map of where I am.

(Condition) The user can catch pokemon

As a logged in user, I can catch a pokemon if I have pokeballs
As a logged in user, I can catch pokemon if I have internet connection
As a logged in user, I can use items to help catch pokemon
If I cleck on the pokeball, I can open the settings menu
If I interact with the settings in this menu I can go to a sectond menu with further settings

(Condition) The user can interact with environment

As a logged in user & gps linked, user can see pokemon and open pokemon, shop, item and pokedex
As a logged in user & gps linked, user can see gyms and open
As a logged in user & gps linked, user can see pokestops and open
As a logged in user & gps linked, user can see pokemon from other people's lures
As a logged in user & gps linked, user can see pokemon from your own lure
As a logged in user & gps linked, user can see your inscence

